org.onyxplatform.api.java

Class OnyxVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.onyxplatform.api.java.OnyxVector
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Catalog, FlowConditions, Lifecycles, Triggers, Windows

    public class OnyxVector
extends java.lang.Object
    Serves as a base for any Onyx concept that is represented by a vector of onyx maps, e.g. windows, triggers, etc.
